title: Drawn to Speed - The Automotive Art of John Lander (2015) Gooner
description:
Drawn to Speed - The Automotive Art of John Lander (2015) (Pdf & Epub) Gooner

Publisher: McFarland (June 2, 2015)
Language: English
ISBN-10: 0786497858
ISBN-13: 978-0786497850

For automotive artist John Lander, cars are more than just transportation: "Some are beautiful examples of rolling sculpture. I try to do more than just draw Fopretty pictures of cars; I include interesting people, backgrounds, and try to set a mood or tell a story." The work of years, this collection of Lander's vintage car art includes more than 100 color illustrations with a short description, including comments by the artist, for each picture
